    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-03-18T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-03-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="119"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d119">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Uhl</persName> to Baron <persName
                            type="to">Fava</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-03-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 18, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Baron</hi>: I inclose herewith for your further
                    information in regard to the Colorado incident copy of a telegram received from
                        <pb facs="0209" n="943" xml:id="pg_943"/> Governor McIntire, dated the 17th
                    instant, stating that he has issued a proclamation offering a reward of $1,000
                    for the apprehension and conviction of the guilty parties.</p>
                <p>Very truly, yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Edwin F. Uhl</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <frus:attachment>
                    <opener>
                        <seg rendition="#center">[Inclosure—Telegram.]</seg>
                    </opener>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">Governor <persName type="from">McIntire</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Uhl</persName>.</hi>
                    </head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Denver, Colo.</hi>
                            </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-03-17">
                                <hi rend="italic">March 17, 1895</hi>
                            </date>.</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>Your telegram received. Proper district attorney assures me he will use every
                        means to arrest and convict guilty. I have issued proclamation offering
                        reward of $1,000, the limit under our statutes, for apprehension and
                        conviction of all or any.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Albert W. McIntire</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                                >Governor.</hi>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </frus:attachment>
            </div>
        </body>
